data.description: **Rare find** Beautiful 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom home awaits its new owners. Two story, spacious, open concept floor plan. Kitchen features a large corner pantry and large island overlooking the living and dining rooms. All four bedrooms are nicely sized. One bedroom and one full bath on the first floor, primary bedroom and two additional bedrooms on the second floor. Primary suite with double vanities, garden soaking tub/shower combo, and walk in closet. This home comes equipped with Smart Home automation: Qolsys smart home panel, WiFi thermostat, WiFi enabled deadbolt lock, a doorbell camera, lamp module, USB outlets in kitchen and Alexa Dot for voice control or control your home on your smartphone. Large, fully fenced in backyard is perfect for entertaining! Flood Zone X and has never flooded. Don't let this one pass you by, call today to schedule your showing!
